name: Pongs Squad - The Myz
description:
Pongs Squad is a group of criminals from an unknown country. They are scattered in various parts of the world due to a dispute between their captain and vice-captain.

Chad Walton is the vice-captain of this group. He was nicknamed the myz (which means the mysterious). His skin was deformed because during an attack on a chemical laboratory in Germany, he was exposed to spiritual spray from the laboratory security guard so that his skin was blistered and could not return to normal. Currently, he is hiding somewhere in Russia.
